          <summary>What is Evident Technologies?</summary>
          <div class="faq-item__answer">
            <p>Evident Technologies builds forensic-grade evidence processing systems designed for legal professionals, oversight bodies, and institutions that require immutable records, deterministic analysis, and reproducible exports.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Who is the platform designed for?</summary>
          <div class="faq-item__answer">
            <p>Legal teams, law enforcement agencies, compliance departments, government auditors, and any professional or organization that needs court-defensible evidence workflows with full chain-of-custody documentation.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>What makes Evident different from standard document management?</summary>
          <div class="faq-item__answer">
            <p>Standard document systems allow edits and deletions. Evident enforces immutability — originals cannot be modified, every action is logged in append-only audit trails, and all outputs are cryptographically verified against source material.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

      </div>
